Quote: We are now in the thick of the cross examination. by Sheehan of the chiefest of the apostles -  Tizzey the Tanner (ko Tanera). ... We have not found anything that can be called a rat; nor even got the scent very strong. But I must not report upon Heret[aunga]. [Tizzy = 6d: a play on Tanner's surname.]
